lp t sn g. Lp t sn g ng quy trnh, ng cch khng ch lm tng tnh thm m cho sn nh m cn gip sn thm vng chc, n nh, khng pht ra ting ku v  bn cao.\n\n\n\nDi y, chng ti s hng dn bn v quy trnh thi cng<strong>lp t sn g cng nghip </strong> mt c c mt cng trnh hon ho:\n\n\n\n<a href=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-576 size-full\" src=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-2.jpg 600w, http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-2-300x214.jpg 300w\" alt=\"thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-2\" width=\"600\" height=\"428\" /></a>\n\n\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<h3><strong>Trc khi thc hin lp t sn g, bn cn phi kim tra v m bo cc tiu ch sau:</strong></h3>\n\n1. Chun b y  sn g cng nghip v cc cng c, dng c cn thit cho qu trnh lp t sn g cng nghiptrc khi tin hnh thi cng. Lu  l vi sn g bn nn <strong>chn mua sn g cng nghip</strong> sau  chuyn n ni cn lp t trc t nht 24h  chng thch nghi vi mi trng trc khi c lp t.\n\n\n\n2. V nhit  mi trng: Hy m bo rng nhit  mi trng lp t ti thiu l19 C v nhit  b mt ti thiu l16 C,  m mi trng t 50% n 75% s l hp l.\n\n\n\n3. Chun b   cm in  dng cho my ct, my khoan vi ngun in~ 210V-220V.\n\n\n\n4. c chng lm sao m bo mp di cnhca nh bn cch mt nn mt khong: ti thiu15mm i vi sn dy 8mm vti thiu19mm i vi sn dy 12mm.\n\n<h3><strong>Quy trnh thi cng lp t sn g cng nghip</strong></h3>\n\nQu trnh thi cng lp t sn g cng nghip gm 3 cng onchnh: lp t vn sn g; kt thc sn; lp t pho chn tng\n\n\n\ny lcng onu tin v cng l quan trng nht m bo cho tnh thm m cng nh  bn chc cho nn nh mi nh bn. Cng onny gm kh nhiubc nh.\n\n\n\nB1:Kim tra v x l mt sn:\n\n\n\nTrc khi lp t, b mt nn phi c lm phng, sch s v m bo  kh, cng b mt. V vy, cn x l nhng ch nn cn g gh  chng tht phng , sau  th lm sch.\n\n\n\n<a href=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-21.jpg\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-2803 aligncenter\" src=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-21.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 616px) 100vw, 616px\" srcset=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-21.jpg 616w, http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-21-300x225.jpg 300w, http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-21-315x236.jpg 315w\" alt=\"thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-2\" width=\"616\" height=\"462\" /></a>\n\n\n\nB2: Tri lp lt sn:\n\n\n\nLp <strong>lt sn g</strong> c tc dng chng m cho sn g v hn ch ting n do vn sn g gy ra trong qu trnh s dng. Khi tri tm lt, b mt c trng nilon phi tri xung mt di v cch st chn tng khong 40mm. Dng bng keo  dnh gia 2 lp lt vi nhau hoc c th t chng chng m ln nhau.\n\n\n\n<img class=\" size-full wp-image-2804 aligncenter\" src=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-22.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 616px) 100vw, 616px\" srcset=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-22.jpg 616w, http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-22-300x225.jpg 300w, http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-22-315x236.jpg 315w\" alt=\"thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao-22\" width=\"616\" height=\"462\" />\n\n\n\nB3: Tin hnh lp t sn g cng nghip:\n\n\n\nHy bt u ghp t gc tri ca cn phng, cc tm <strong>vn sn g cng nghip</strong> phi lun lt theo chiu ca ngun sng  lm ni vn g v cc mp ni u mi thanh g c ghp so le nhau. m bo duy tr khong cch gia mp chn tng vi sn g cng nh khong cch gia cc tm vn sn g khong 10mm  ghp mng cho tm cui cng v cng l khong cch an ton cho vic dn n ca sn g.\n\n\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-492 \" src=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep6.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 602px) 100vw, 602px\" srcset=\"http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep6.jpg 500w, http://sangocongnghiepcaocap.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep6-300x172.jpg 300w\" alt=\"thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep\" width=\"602\" height=\"347\" />\n\n<ul>\n\n 	<li><em>Kt thc sn</em></li>\n\n</ul>\n\nVic cui cng ca thi cng <strong>sn gcng nghip</strong> l dng np  kt thc sn vitm ghp cui cng. m bo khong cch gia tm ghp cui cng vi chn tng, che kn khong cch  bi pho chn tng hoc np kt thc.\n\n<ul>\n\n 	<li><em>Lp pho chn tng</em></li>\n\n</ul>\n\nPho chn tng ph bin hin nay l pho g MDF ph vn g. Chngc c nh vi chn tng bng inh chuyn dng ng pho. Cui cng l tin hnh kim tra li ton b sn mt lt, tra keo silicon vo nhng khe h st vi tng v khung ca.\n\n\n\nKt thc lp t sn, by gi bn hy dn dp sch s v nh gi xem sn g p v c tnh thm m cha nh!\n\n\n\nNu bn khng th t lp t sn g cng nghip th c th lin h vi cc cng ty, ca hng phn phi sn g. Cng ty sn g Thy S phn phi v nhn thi cng lp t sn g cng nghip gi r nht. Vi i ng thi cng sn g chuyn nghip, giu kinh nghim trong vic thi cng lp t sn g, chng ti cam kt cung cp dch v tt nht, em li nhng sn phm p nht, bn nht cho khch hng.','Thi cng lp t sn g cng nghip nh th no?','','publish','open','open','','thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-nhu-the-nao','','','2018-02-24 10:39:00','2018-02-24 03:39:00','',0,'https://bizhostvn.com/w/noithat2/?p=455',0,'post','',0),(456,2,'2018-02-24 10:38:56','2018-02-24 03:38:56','','light-wood-flooring-632x348','','inherit','open','closed','','light-wood-flooring-632x348','','','2018-02-24 10:38:56','2018-02-24 03:38:56','',455,'https://bizhostvn.com/w/noithat2/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/light-wood-flooring-632x348.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(458,2,'2018-02-24 10:40:40','2018-02-24 03:40:40','Cng ty Sn p c trn 12 nm kinh nghim thi cng lp t sn g cng nghip, sn g t nhin, sn g ngoi tri, sn nha ti H Ni.\n\n\n\ni ng th lp t sn g lnh ngh c o to bi bn,  chuyn thi cng sn g cho cc cng trnh cht lng cao, thm m p. Cng ty c phn Sn p khng s dng th khng chuyn gi ngoi th trng nh cc ca hng sn g nh trn cc tuyn ng: Trng Chinh,  La Thnh, Hong Quc Vit, Minh Khai ...\n\n\n\n<img src=\"http://sango.us/sites/default/files/u10/thi-cong-lap-dat-san-cong-nghiep_0.jpg\" alt=\"thi cng lp t sn g cng nghip ti h ni\" width=\"550\" height=\"462\" />\n\n\n\nLp t sn g cng nghip\n\n\n\n thi cng lp t sn g cng nghipng tiu chun do nh sn xut a ra, th lp t phi m bo nhng tiu ch sau:\n\n\n\nMt ct nn phi v sinh sch s, phng v kh ro. Sau khi v sinh mt nn xong th lp t c th chi mt lp xp nilon (foan xp bng, foan xp, lt cao su)  chng m v lm phng m mt sn, sn g lp ln trn lp foan trng m ny phi cch tng 8-12mm. y l khe h  g dn n t 3-5mm. Nu khng  khe gin n ny sn g nh bn s b phng ln, bp bnh, cp knh, c th gy nguy him cho bn v gia nh.\n\n\n\nLu :\n\n<div>Khi th lp np  ca ra vo, bn phi yu cu th bt vt  np xung mt nn tht cht sau  mi sp mt nn ln trn.</div>\n\n<div>Khch hng lu  khi lp sn g xong phi yu cu ly phiu bo hnh.</div>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n\n\n<img src=\"http://sango.us/sites/default/files/u10/san-go-kahn.jpg\" alt=\"sn g cng nghip\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\" />\n\n\n\nSn g cng nghip kahn\n\n\n\nThng thng, khi bn gi in hi gi sn g, bn s nhn c bo gi vt liu g v gi hon thin. Hin nay, vi cc cng ty ln nh Sn p cung cp c vt liu t vn sn, xp lt v ph kin, chng ti cung cp c dch v thi cng lp t. Do  chi ph <strong><em>gi nhn cng lp t sn g</em></strong> s thp hn khch t thu th v lp t. Gi lp t sn g hin nay giao ng t 30.000 tr ln. V vy, chng ti khuyn bn khi mua sn g, hy chn nhng cng ty, i l ln v uy tn v chn c dch v lp t  m bo quyn li bo hnh v sa cha ca mnh khi c bt l li hng no xy ra trong qu trnh sinh hot v s dng.','Chuyn thi cng lp t sn g cng nghip ti H Ni','','publish','open','open','','chuyen-thi-cong-lap-dat-san-go-cong-nghiep-tai-ha-noi','','','2018-02-24 10:40:40','2018-02-24 03:40:40','',0,'https://bizhostvn.com/w/noithat2/?p=458',0,'post','',0),(459,2,'2018-02-24 10:40:35','2018-02-24 03:40:35','','san-nhua-gia-re','','inherit','open','closed','','san-nhua-gia-re','','','2018-02-24 10:40:35','2018-02-24 03:40:35','',458,'https://bizhostvn.com/w/noithat2/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/san-nhua-gia-re.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(461,2,'2018-02-24 10:42:06','2018-02-24 03:42:06','<div><span data-mce-mark=\"1\">Sn g ngy cng c s dng rng ri, khng ch trong khng gian gia nh m cn  cc ca hng, trung tm thng mi. V sn g a dng v chng loi nn ty vo tng khng gian m chng ta chn loi sn g cho ph hp. Vy vi khng gian phng ng th nn chn loi sn g no? Cng tham kho cch chn sn g cho phng ng di y nh!</span></div>\n\n<div><span data-mce-mark=\"1\"><strong>1. L do nn lp t sn g cho phng ng</strong></span></div>\n\n<span data-mce-mark=\"1\">Phng ng l khng gian khng ch i hi s sch s m cn phi yn tnh bi v n c nh hng n gic ng v sc khe ca gia ch. Phng ng ngoi trang b nhng  dng cn thit nh ging, t qun o, bn trang im, bn hc th cn c trang tr bi cc  ni tht nh rm ca, sn g, giy dn tng\n\n\n\n<img src=\"http://sango.us/sites/default/files/u10/lua-chon-mau-san-go-cong-nghiep-cho-phong-ngu1.jpg\" alt=\"sn g cng nghip lp cho phng ng\" width=\"500\" height=\"297\" /></span>\n\n<div><span data-mce-mark=\"1\">\n\nS d nn lp t sn g cho phng ng l v sn g c dng  lt nn to cm gic sch s khi bc chn ln sn. Sn g c ch to t nhng nguyn liu an ton cho sc khe nn khng gy hi ti sc khe ngi s dng. Ngoi ra, sn g c nhiu chng loi, mu sc c th lm cho phng ng tr nn n tng hn. c bit, vi nhng gam mu du nh s mang li cm gic thoi mi cho gia ch.</span></div>\n\n<div><span data-mce-mark=\"1\">Nh vy, sn g phng ng khng ch c tc dng lm p phng m n cn gip gia ch cm thy thoi mi hn v tinh thn, ng s ngon gic hn.</span></div>\n\n<div><strong>2. Cch chn sn g cho phng ng</strong></div>\n\n<div><span data-mce-mark=\"1\"> chn c loi sn g ph hp nht cho phng ng th bn c th da trn mt s tiu ch sau:\n\n</span>\n\n<strong><span data-mce-mark=\"1\"> dy sn g:</span></strong></div>\n\nXt v  dy sn g th sn g c 2 loi chnh gm 1 loi dy 8mm v 1 loi dy 12mm. Vi khng gian phng ng th bn nn chn loi sn g 8mm. Bi v phng ng khng c nhiu ngi i li, tn sut s dng cng t nn khng cn thit phi s dng loi sn g c  chu lc cao nh sn g 12mm.\n\n<img src=\"http://sango.us/sites/default/files/u10/san-go-phong-ngu_0.jpg\" alt=\"sn g cng nghip phng ng\" width=\"500\" height=\"284\" />\n\n\n\n<em>Sn g phng ng mang li cm gic m p, sch s (2)</em>\n\n\n\n<strong>c tnh sn g:</strong>\n\nPhng ng i hi mt mi trng trong lnh, kh thong, an ton cho sc khe nn loi sn g thch hp cho phng ng phi c cht lng tt. Bn nn chn sn g c sn xut t nguyn liu t nhin, khng c cht c hi. u im ca sn g cng nghip l c c tnh chng chu nc, chng m mc  gi cho nn nh lun kh thong.\n\n\n\n<strong><span data-mce-mark=\"1\">Mu sc sn g:</span></strong>\n\n<div><span data-mce-mark=\"1\">Vi phng ng th bn nn chn loi san go c mu ti hn mu sn tng  to chiu su cho cn phng. Nhng khng nn chn mu ti qu nh mu en hay mu sng qu nh mu trng s mang li cm gic bt an cho gia ch. Mu sc sn g phng ng thng c nhiu ngi s dng nht  l gam mu vng, vng nht, mu nu, cc tong mu t nhin</span></div>\n\n<div><span data-mce-mark=\"1\">Ngoi ra, bn cng cn lu  nn chn sn g c vn g n gin, khng nn qu cu k, gy ri mt to cm gic cht chi cho cn phng.</span></div>\n\n<div><span data-mce-mark=\"1\">Hy vng qua bi vit trn, cc bn s chn c loi sn g ph hp nht cho phng ng nh mnh  lm mi cn phng.</span></div>','Chn sn g cho phng ng th no ph hp?','','publish','open','open','','chon-san-go-cho-phong-ngu-the-nao-phu-hop','','','2018-02-24 10:42:06','2018-02-24 03:42:06','',0,'https://